Cyberpunk style: A neon-lit digital mailroom floating in cyberspace, featuring translucent holographic envelopes being dissected by laser beams that reveal layers of glowing data streams and code fragments inside. Mechanical arms with fiber optic cables sort through floating message packets, each one splitting apart to show nested components like Russian dolls - headers, body content, and attachments visualized as distinct geometric shapes in electric blue, magenta, and cyan. The scene is set against a dark grid-lined void with distant server towers pulsing with light. Rain-slicked surfaces reflect the neon glow, and small particles of data float like digital dust motes through the air. The composition emphasizes the act of peeling back layers and examining hidden structures within digital communications.
